SMTP Service Extension for
Authentication
1999", shape=ellipse, URL="RFC2554.html", target="_top", tooltip="This document defines an SMTP service extension [ESMTP] whereby an SMTP client may indicate an authentication mechanism to the server, perform an authentication protocol exchange, and optionally negotiate a security layer for subsequent protocol interactions. [STANDARDS-TRACK]"];
